{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/create-a-block-element-bootstrap-button","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Kreiranje Bootstrap dugmeta blok elementa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Obično, tvoji elementi <code>button</code> sa klasama <code>btn</code> i <code>btn-default</code> imaju širinu jednaku samo tekstu koji sadrže. Na primer:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;button class=\"btn btn-default\">Submit&#x3C;/button>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo dugme bi imalo širinu jednaku samo reči <code>Submit</code>.</p>\n<p><button class='btn btn-default'>Submit</button></p>\n<p>Kada ga učinite blok elementom dodavanjem dodatne klase <code>btn-block</code>, tvoje dugme će se protezati da popuni ceo raspoloživi prostor na tvom sajtu, a svi sledeći elementi će ići u \"novi red\" ispod tog bloka.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;button class=\"btn btn-default btn-block\">Submit&#x3C;/button>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo dugme bi zauzelo 100% raspoložive širine.</p>\n<p><button class='btn btn-default btn-block'>Submit</button></p>\n<p>Zapamti da i dalje zahtevaju klasu <code>btn</code>.</p>\n<p>Dodaj Bootstrap klasu <code>btn-block</code> na tvoje Bootstrap dugme.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348cd8acef08812","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16810,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/create-a-block-element-bootstrap-button"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://font